<ab facs="#facs_149_r2l3">dann bey vns <expan>geweſe<ex>n</ex></expan> ſeit geredt <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / von des Pannes <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan> / gen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_149_r2l4">C . Molitor / vnd <expan>Eb<ex>erhard</ex></expan> <expan>Lochn<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>Burg<ex>er</ex>n</expan> / . vnd ſie <expan>yecʒund<ex>e</ex>n</expan> Jr botſchaft </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_149_r2l5"><expan>ſelb<ex>er</ex></expan> darvmb cʒü ew ſchıcken / Alſo <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> / daʒ Jr Jn ewr brief vnd </ab>
