<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Lieb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>, als etliche <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
                        rates yeczunden hie czü <expan>Nür<ex>emberg</ex></expan> mit ew, als ir
                        dann bey uns <expan>gewese<ex>n</ex></expan> seit, geredt
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> von des pannes
                            <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan> gen <expan>C<ex>onrad</ex></expan> Molitor
                        und <expan>Eb<ex>erhard</ex></expan>
<expan>Lochn<ex>er</ex></expan>, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex>n</expan>, und sie <expan>yeczund<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        ir botschaft <expan>selb<ex>er</ex></expan> darumb czü ew schicken, also
                                <expan>ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir in ewr brief und fürdrung an
                                    <add><expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan></add>
<expan>richt<ex>er</ex></expan> gen Erfürt <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        wöllet und durch <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> willen darczü tün und
                        bestellen, daz die <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> aws
                            <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan> panne gelassen
                            <expan>werd<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und fürbas <add>damit</add> ungemüwet
                            <add>und unbeswert</add>
<expan>beleib<ex>e</ex>n</expan>. Als etc. und das
                            <expan>allcz<ex>eit</ex></expan> etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> in
                        die <expan>s<ex>an</ex>c<ex>t</ex>i</expan>
<expan>Pet<ex>ri</ex></expan> ad <expan>vinc<ex>u</ex>la<ex>m</ex></expan>
                        etc.</ab>
</div>
